  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, turmeric, paprika, and salt. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Saskatoon berries and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Add the maple syrup and lemon juice. Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, stirring occasionally, until the sauce has thickened and the berries have broken down, about 20 minutes.",
